title: Los Angeles/Eastside
name: Cafe NELA
directions: Corner of Cypress Avenue and Macon Street (1 block west of Division street)
hours: Thursday-Saturday 8PM-1AM, Sunday afternoon varies - see website.
content: Music Venue and Beer Bar specializing in Punk Rock, Hard Rock, Jazz, and experimental music; featuring local bands and touring acts from Latin America, Asia, Australia, Europe, Canada, and the US. Beer only. 21 and over
